Class StatisticsController.PURow

java.lang.Object
controllers.StatisticsController.PURow
Enclosing class:
StatisticsController
public static class StatisticsController.PURow extends Object
View-model representing product usage by inventory item for a given period. Used to populate both the product usage table and bar chart.
